CONVERSATION TITLE: Microsoft, Canada Invitation to apply for Software Engineer Intern role!
SUBJECT: Microsoft, Canada Invitation to apply for Software Engineer Intern role!
CONTENT: Hi Gaurav,   My name is Sonia and I am a Talent Sourcer with Microsoft, Canada. I am reaching out because after reviewing your experience, I believe you would be a great fit at Microsoft as a Software Engineer intern in Summer 2024 with the Coalition Team. The Coalition is a flagship first-party studio within Xbox Game Studios and the home to one of gaming‚Äôs most critically and commercially acclaimed series, Gears of War. As a studio, we lead from our values and work together to promote respect and inclusion, a growth mindset and grit, all while putting our team first. This is an opportunity to explore‚ÄØan interest in gaming and work on cutting-edge technology at a world renowned studio.   Please note this role is based out of Vancouver, BC. Vancouver, BC is the only location we have available at this time. We will not be able to change the location you are being considered for.   If you are interested in this opportunity, please apply online and let me know once your application has been submitted. One of our recruiters will be looking at your application and we will contact you directly with additional information if you're selected to move forward in our interview process.   Here's the link to apply and learn more:  https://jobs.careers.microsoft.com/global/en/job/1684262/Software-Engineer%3A-Internship-Opportunities-for-University-Students%2C-Vancouver%2C-BC  We will be finalizing the candidates for the interviews soon, so if you are interested, do apply ASAP.  I look forward to hearing from you!   Best Regards,  Sonia  Sonia Chawla University Recruiter at Microsoft
